   <p xml:id="1" begin="00:00:09.538" end="00:00:11.941">&gt;&gt; GETTING YOUNG KIDS TO</p>
   <p xml:id="2" begin="00:00:10.172" end="00:00:12.908">READ AND BEING POLITE</p>
