   <p xml:id="9" begin="00:00:21.383" end="00:00:23.519">MR. PATTERSON CAME UP WITH</p>
   <p xml:id="10" begin="00:00:22.017" end="00:00:23.786">THE IDEA AND HE JOINS US</p>
