   <p xml:id="21" begin="00:00:32.728" end="00:00:36.932">&gt;&gt; RIGHT.</p>
   <p xml:id="22" begin="00:00:33.295" end="00:00:37.933">&gt;&gt; AND I LIKE THE IDEA OF</p>
   <p xml:id="23" begin="00:00:37.066" end="00:00:39.235">PEOPLE GETTING TOGETHER THAT</p>
