   <p xml:id="27" begin="00:00:42.138" end="00:00:43.839">TRY TO MOVE IT FORWARD.</p>
   <p xml:id="28" begin="00:00:43.172" end="00:00:44.840">&gt;&gt; RIGHT.</p>
   <p xml:id="29" begin="00:00:43.973" end="00:00:46.208">IT DIDN'T HURT THAT YOU AND</p>
